The evidence with the title 'These 8 men are richer than 3.6 billion people combined ' says Jan 17, 2017  ... Eight men now control as much wealth as the world's poorest 3.6  ... Financial leaders and some of the wealthiest people in the world. Eight men now control as much wealth as half of the world's population.  ... And over the past 25 years, the top 1% has gained more income than the bottom 50% put together. 
